OL,3,CPensioner claims she fractured
OL,4,Cshoulder in fall after pothole inaction
OL,6,FA pensioner who claims she fractured
OL,7,Fher shoulder after falling into a
OL,8,Fpothole has been told she is not
OL,9,Fentitled to compensation as Jersey law
OL,10,Fdoes not force the authorities to pay
OL,11,Fout, even if they are at fault.
OL,13,FJanet Turner was walking her dog along
OL,14,FLa Ruette d'Avranches in St Lawrence
OL,15,Fjust before Christmas when she fell.
OL,17,FShe explains: "It's a lane I've walked
OL,18,Ffor 40 years and never had any
OL,19,Fproblems. All of a sudden, I've found
OL,20,Fmyself sitting in a very wet pothole
OL,21,Fwhich I tripped in.
