OL,6,F"It was horrible, I couldn't feel my
OL,7,Fhand at all - it wouldn't work."
OL,9,FJanet went to A&E and was found to
OL,10,Fhave fractured her right shoulder with
OL,11,Fextensive bruising on her right side.
OL,13,FJanet's husband Michael contacted
OL,14,Flocal officials and says the Parish
OL,15,FRoads Committee were aware of the
OL,16,Fpotholes and planned to fill them in,
OL,17,Fbut the work had not started yet.
OL,19,FConvinced they had a negligence claim,
OL,20,FMichael approached the Parish of St
OL,21,FLawrence.
