OL,6,FHe says: "I took all the photographs
OL,7,Fto the Parish Hall and the Constable
OL,8,Fthen sent them to their insurance
OL,9,Fcompany. They wrote back and said,
OL,10,F'You've got no chance of any
OL,11,Fcompensation'.
OL,13,F"That upset me because since December,
OL,14,Ftwice and then once a week now, I've
OL,15,Ftaken Janet to the hospital for
OL,16,Ftreatment and back again."
