OL,6,FIn response to the situation, St
OL,7,FLawrence Constable Deidre Mezbourian
OL,8,Fsays: "I understand that somebody did
OL,9,Funfortunately injure themselves and as
OL,10,Fwith any parish or public body, we
OL,11,Fhave to carry full insurance.
OL,13,F"In this instance, it was referred to
OL,14,Four insurers for how to proceed and
OL,15,Fthat decision was recommended to us by
OL,16,Fthe insurance company."
