OL,6,FJanet has thanked the hospital staff
OL,7,Ffor their compassion and support with
OL,8,Fher rehabilitation, but the couple
OL,9,Fwant a change in the law so that
OL,10,Frelevant authorities are held liable
OL,11,Ffor similar situations in the future,
OL,12,Fas already happens in the UK.
OL,14,FAdvocate George Pearce from BCR Law
OL,15,Fsays the question of compensation has
OL,16,Fbeen debated over the years, but it is
OL,17,Fnot currently covered under Jersey
OL,18,Flegislation.
