OL,4,Cshoulder in fall after pothole inaction
OL,6,F"Action in the UK is limited by the
OL,7,Ffact that if the Highway Authority
OL,8,Ftook reasonable steps to correct the
OL,9,Fdefect but the accident happened
OL,10,Fnonetheless, then they will be
OL,11,Fprotected in those circumstances.
OL,13,F"I know it's a question that is
OL,14,Freigniting, so we'll have to watch
OL,15,Fthis space as to whether or not there
OL,16,Fwill be any legislative changes in
OL,17,FJersey which will allow people to
OL,18,Fbring claims in future."
